Naomi Grossman https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Naomi_Grossman 0 Naomi Grossman (born February 6, 1975) is an American actress, writer, and producer best known for her role as Pepper in the second and fourth seasons and also as Satanist Cardinal Samantha Crowe in the eighth season of the FX horror television series American Horror Story.
